                            <fo:block-container page-break-after="avoid" font-size="2em" line-height="1.1em" space-after="0.5em" margin-left="0" margin-right="0" space-before="0" role="H1" id="ariaid-title4"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0"><fo:marker marker-class-name="chaptertitle-only"><fo:inline/> <!--content(text)--><fo:inline>1. Objectif de la documentation</fo:inline></fo:marker><fo:marker marker-class-name="chaptertitle-no-prefix"><fo:inline/> 2 - <!--content(text)--><fo:inline>1. Objectif de la documentation</fo:inline></fo:marker><fo:marker marker-class-name="chaptertitle"><fo:inline/> | 2 - <!--content(text)--><fo:inline>1. Objectif de la documentation</fo:inline></fo:marker><fo:inline>Chapter 2. </fo:inline><fo:inline>1. Objectif de la documentation</fo:inline></fo:block></fo:block-container>
                            <fo:block-container space-after="0" margin-left="0" margin-right="0" space-before="0"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0">
                                <fo:block-container space-after="1em" max-width="100%"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0"><fo:inline><fo:external-graphic src="file:/C:/Users/Charl%C3%A8ne/Pictures/John-Deere2026/media/s_sunflower_coverpage.png?" fox:alt-text="image moissonneuse-batteuse" max-width="100%" scaling="uniform" width="908in div 96" content-width="scale-to-fit" height="526in div 96" content-height="scale-to-fit"/></fo:inline></fo:block></fo:block-container>
                                <fo:block-container space-after="0.5em" margin-left="0" margin-right="0" space-before="1em"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0"><fo:inline font-weight="bold">John Deere Werke
                                    Zweibrücken</fo:inline></fo:block></fo:block-container>
                                <fo:block-container space-after="0.5em" margin-left="0" margin-right="0" space-before="1em"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0">Ce
                                    manuel décrit la configuration et le réglage d'une
                                    moissonneuse-batteuse série S avant la récolte de tournesols. Il
                                    présente les composants et réglages clés pour améliorer les
                                    performances et la qualité des grains dans les conditions
                                    spécifiques à cette culture.</fo:block></fo:block-container>
                                <fo:block-container space-after="0.5em" margin-left="0" margin-right="0" space-before="1em"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0">Les réglages proposés sont des points de départ à affiner selon
                                    les conditions de terrain et la teneur en humidité. La section
                                        <fo:inline color="rgb(51 , 122 , 183)"><fo:inline font-weight="bold"><fo:basic-link show-destination="new" indicate-destination="true" internal-destination="unique_5" fox:alt-text="« Conseils et astuces »">« Conseils et astuces
                                        »</fo:basic-link></fo:inline><fo:basic-link show-destination="new" indicate-destination="true" internal-destination="unique_5" fox:alt-text=" "><fo:inline font-style="italic"><fo:basic-link show-destination="new" indicate-destination="true" fox:alt-text=" " internal-destination="unique_5"> (on page </fo:basic-link><fo:basic-link show-destination="new" indicate-destination="true" fox:alt-text=" " internal-destination="unique_5"><fo:page-number-citation ref-id="unique_5"/></fo:basic-link><fo:basic-link show-destination="new" indicate-destination="true" fox:alt-text=" " internal-destination="unique_5">)</fo:basic-link></fo:inline></fo:basic-link></fo:inline>
                                    et le système embarqué de réglage interactif (si équipé) vous
                                    aideront à les préciser.</fo:block></fo:block-container>
                            </fo:block></fo:block-container>
                        </fo:block></fo:block-container>
                        </fo:block></fo:block></fo:block-container></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block-container></fo:block></fo:block-container></fo:block></fo:flow></fo:page-sequence><fo:page-sequence master-reference="chapter" force-page-count="no-force" line-height-shift-adjustment="disregard-shifts"><fo:static-content flow-name="sc-before-left" role="artifact"><fo:table border-collapse="separate" table-layout="fixed" width="100%"><fo:table-body><fo:table-row><!--TOP-LEFT--><fo:table-cell start-indent="0" end-indent="0" height="1in" width="(8.5in - 1in - 1in)" text-align="left" display-align="center" font-size="10pt" font-family="Roboto , sans-serif"><fo:block><fo:retrieve-marker retrieve-class-name="maptitle" retrieve-boundary="document" retrieve-position="first-including-carryover"/><fo:retrieve-marker retrieve-class-name="parttitle" retrieve-boundary="document" retrieve-position="first-including-carryover"/><fo:retrieve-marker retrieve-class-name="chaptertitle" retrieve-boundary="document" retrieve-position="first-including-carryover"/><fo:retrieve-marker retrieve-class-name="sectiontitle" retrieve-boundary="document" retrieve-position="first-including-carryover"/> | <fo:page-number/></fo:block></fo:table-cell></fo:table-row></fo:table-body></fo:table></fo:static-content><fo:static-content flow-name="sc-before-right" role="artifact"><fo:table border-collapse="separate" table-layout="fixed" width="100%"><fo:table-body><fo:table-row><!--TOP-RIGHT--><fo:table-cell start-indent="0" end-indent="0" height="1in" width="(8.5in - 1in - 1in)" text-align="right" display-align="center" font-size="10pt" font-family="Roboto , sans-serif"><fo:block><fo:retrieve-marker retrieve-class-name="maptitle" retrieve-boundary="document" retrieve-position="first-including-carryover"/><fo:retrieve-marker retrieve-class-name="parttitle" retrieve-boundary="document" retrieve-position="first-including-carryover"/><fo:retrieve-marker retrieve-class-name="chaptertitle" retrieve-boundary="docum