                            <fo:block-container page-break-after="avoid" font-size="2em" line-height="1.1em" space-after="0.5em" margin-left="0" margin-right="0" space-before="0" role="H1" id="ariaid-title21"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0"><fo:marker marker-class-name="chaptertitle-only"><fo:inline/> <!--content(text)--><fo:inline>Pour aller plus loin</fo:inline></fo:marker><fo:marker marker-class-name="chaptertitle-no-prefix"><fo:inline/> 10 - <!--content(text)--><fo:inline>Pour aller plus loin</fo:inline></fo:marker><fo:marker marker-class-name="chaptertitle"><fo:inline/> | 10 - <!--content(text)--><fo:inline>Pour aller plus loin</fo:inline></fo:marker><fo:inline>Chapter 10. </fo:inline><fo:inline>Pour aller plus loin</fo:inline></fo:block></fo:block-container>
                            <fo:block-container space-after="0" margin-left="0" margin-right="0" space-before="0"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0">
                                <fo:block-container space-after="0.5em" margin-left="0" margin-right="0" space-before="1em"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0">Télécharger l'application GoHarvest pour plus d'informations
                                    sur les réglages, le calculateur de perte, JDParts, les vidéos,
                                    les procédures …</fo:block></fo:block-container>
                                <fo:block-container space-after="1em" max-width="100%"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0"><fo:inline><fo:external-graphic src="file:/C:/Users/Charl%C3%A8ne/Pictures/John-Deere2026/media/Capture%20d'%C3%A9cran%202026-02-02%20123417.png" fox:alt-text="site" max-width="100%" scaling="uniform" width="637in div 96" content-width="scale-to-fit" height="231in div 96" content-height="scale-to-fit"/></fo:inline></fo:block></fo:block-container>
                                <fo:block-container space-after="0.5em" margin-left="0" margin-right="0" space-before="1em"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0">Cliquer sur le lien de GoHarvest sur YouTube pour consulter des
                                    vidéos détaillées sur la procédure de mise hors tension,
                                    CombineAdvisor, Active Terrain Adjustment et bien plus
                                    encore.</fo:block></fo:block-container>
                                <fo:block-container space-after="0.5em" margin-left="0" margin-right="0" space-before="1em"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0">(https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3KR77OTdNKU&amp;list=PL1KGsSJ4C
                                    Wk7jzH744F1bByhwXWAlxmFj )</fo:block></fo:block-container>
                                <fo:block-container space-after="1em" max-width="100%"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0"><fo:inline><fo:external-graphic src="file:/C:/Users/Charl%C3%A8ne/Pictures/John-Deere2026/media/Capture%20d'%C3%A9cran%202026-02-02%20123427.png" fox:alt-text="image GoHarvest" max-width="100%" scaling="uniform" width="570in div 96" content-width="scale-to-fit" height="306in div 96" content-height="scale-to-fit"/></fo:inline></fo:block></fo:block-container>
                            </fo:block></fo:block-container>
                        </fo:block></fo:block-container>
                    </fo:block>
                </fo:block></fo:block-container>
            </fo:block>
        </fo:block></fo:block-container>
    </fo:block></fo:block-container>
